  "page": "Dennis the Lame",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Dennis<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Lame</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\"><img alt=\"Poor Fellows.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Poor_Fellows.svg/50px-Poor_Fellows.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Poor_Fellows.svg/75px-Poor_Fellows.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cd/Poor_Fellows.svg/100px-Poor_Fellows.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Dennis_the_Lame_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Dennis the Lame (The Rise of the Dragon).jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Dennis_the_Lame_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/280px-Dennis_the_Lame_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg\" width=\"280\" height=\"560\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Dennis_the_Lame_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/421px-Dennis_the_Lame_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/Dennis_the_Lame_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/561px-Dennis_the_Lame_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Dennis the Lame by Thomas Denmark for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Dennis</b>, known as <b>Dennis the Lame</b>, was a leader of the <a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a> against King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_the_Lame&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Following the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant\" title=\"Faith Militant\">Faith Militant</a>'s defeats in the battles at <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Stonebridge\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle of Stonebridge\">Stonebridge</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_Great_Fork\" title=\"Battle at the Great Fork\">Great Fork of the Blackwater</a> the previous year, new leaders arose across the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/43_AC\" title=\"43 AC\">43&#160;AC</a>, one of which was Dennis the Lame. He and his followers were hardly distinguishable from outlaws, ambushing royal forces then disappearing into the greenwood. <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">Smallfolk</a> gave them aid wherever they went, while the <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> and men-at-arms who were sent out to bring them to justice often disappeared.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The exact region that Dennis the Lame and his followers were active in hasn't been stated. Dennis was still alive at the time of Maegor's death, but his ultimate fate has not been revealed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_the_Lame&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Prince into King - The Ascension of Jaehaerys I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404070536\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.256 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 668/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10555/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7014/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1173/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1586/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.63 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  244.608      1 -total\n 94.61%  231.421      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 94.11%  230.211      1 Template:Infobox\n 1